{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing has happened as far as as the army's behavior was in the first days of their arrival.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians-- the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first thing they did when they arrived?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to the jails, opened the jails, and let all-- all the jailed people out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the first act because in the jail there were plenty of communists, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the first act, together with the communist, all the criminals got out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and then started-- started the process of nationalization, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every manufacturer was in turn visited and-- and-- and the organization in each factory, a nucleus of workers which organized itself as-- as a subunit of the party to-- serving the new masters and the-- and the-- and the communist state.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tried in their own way, in their own unprepared and unrehearsed way, to become public servants and-- and political activists and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I remember seeing very clearly-- well, the factory-- we were told, you run the factory, but it's not yours anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then one day a Russian civilian came to our home, together with the chairman of the committee-- one of our workers that took over the factory.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not-- we were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to go there to-- to-- to formally run it, but we were not the owners anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- we go-- we went to the factory to supervise to make sure that the state is getting everything that they are entitled to, yeah, of nationalized property.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- and then they came to our house and they took an inventory of all the furniture and everything that was in the house, written up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to the-- to the sideboard.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
